Now, leave your stove on for heat
and to boil water for washing.

724
01:15:08,737 --> 01:15:11,570
Here's some spare candles,

725
01:15:11,640 --> 01:15:14,404
yeah, and some-- and some matches.

726
01:15:14,476 --> 01:15:17,377
There you are.
Thank you.

727
01:15:17,446 --> 01:15:21,007
